        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/946/870/medium/606650ca-f241-4e87-a859-0b1e4a5d42b0.png" srcset="" alt="Open Profile Pictures" height="315" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_7CA37F90-E0DC-0138-409E-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>profile pictures </strong>folder.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="delete_profile_picture_1" data-step-uuid="7CA393D0-E0DC-0138-409F-12F2183ABDFB">
    <h3 id="delete_profile_picture_1" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Delete Profile Picture</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/799/976/original/0d650cd8-27fa-4efe-9724-73b0a3e65abd.png" srcset="" alt="Delete Profile Picture" height="270" width="830">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_7CA3BFB0-E0DC-0138-40A1-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the file and click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1]. Then click the <strong>Delete</strong> link [3]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
